arts.ttl: Athletic Bilbao and Girona extend winless streaks with 1-1 draw in Spanish league
arts.sum: Athletic started with three straight victories but then lost three in a row coming into the home match against Girona. Valencia was on its way to its third win in four league matches when it conceded a goal late in stoppage time in a 2-2 draw at Espanyol.
